        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>You attended an event. Write an article for your blog.</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 80 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>Yesterday, I went to a concert ! It was very original because there were not any intruments. It's weird, no?</p>
                <p>Indeed, there were not intruments because the science was in the place. Four persons made music with domestic things. But what ? For exemple, one of this people made music with a glass of water. Another people played with a lot of boils to replace the drum.</p>
                <p>It was very original and magic. The science is able to replace different instruments and products different sounds. So, I have one advice for you... Try a science concert !</p>
            </div>
